      <div class="summary">
  <p>On December 23rd a Muggle employee of the Ministry of Magic released this website to the Muggle Community. Site security is still breached and Wizarding community news is publicised to Muggles for the first time in over 300 years. We are doing everything possible to rectify the situation.</p>
</div>

